lead_paragraph: At the top of the Vikings' shiny, new $1.1 billion football palace, there is a ring of glass separating the seating bowl from the roof that the team and the stadium designers call the "clear story."

headline.print_headline: The Push and Pull Required for $1B Vikings Showplace Is Over
